### Promo Management & Usage

@api_url = http://localhost:8080/v1
@admin_token = {{admin_token}}
@customer_token = {{customer_token}}
@checkout_id = {{checkout_id}}

### 1. [Admin] Create Fixed Amount Promo
POST {{api_url}}/admin/promos
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "code": "GAYAKINI50K",
  "type": "FIXED_AMOUNT",
  "value": 50000,
  "minOrderValue": 200000,
  "usageLimit": 100,
  "startDate": "2024-01-01T00:00:00Z",
  "endDate": "2025-12-31T23:59:59Z",
  "isActive": true
}

> {% client.global.set("promo_id_fixed", response.body.data.id); %}

### 2. [Admin] Create Percentage Promo
POST {{api_url}}/admin/promos
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "code": "DISKON10",
  "type": "PERCENTAGE",
  "value": 10,
  "maxDiscountAmount": 30000,
  "minOrderValue": 100000,
  "usageLimit": 50,
  "startDate": "2024-01-01T00:00:00Z",
  "endDate": "2025-12-31T23:59:59Z",
  "isActive": true
}

> {% client.global.set("promo_id_perc", response.body.data.id); %}

### 3. [Admin] List All Promos
GET {{api_url}}/admin/promos
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

### 4. [Admin] Get Promo Detail
GET {{api_url}}/admin/promos/{{promo_id_fixed}}
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}

### 5. [Admin] Update Promo
PUT {{api_url}}/admin/promos/{{promo_id_fixed}}
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "value": 55000,
  "isActive": true
}

### 6. [Customer] Apply Promo to Checkout
# Ensure you have a valid checkout_id in your environment (from 40-checkout.http)
PUT {{api_url}}/checkouts/{{checkout_id}}/promo
Authorization: Bearer {{customer_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "promoCode": "GAYAKINI50K"
}

### 7. [Customer] Remove Promo from Checkout
DELETE {{api_url}}/checkouts/{{checkout_id}}/promo
Authorization: Bearer {{customer_token}}

### 8. [Admin] Delete Promo
DELETE {{api_url}}/admin/promos/{{promo_id_perc}}
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
